---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Follow by RSS
description: Use RSS if you want new Democratic Justice work without the noise.
permalink: /rss/index.html
ogType: website
kicker: Follow
---
{% set feedUrl = "/feed.xml" | absoluteUrl(site.url) %}
<section class="page-shell page-shell--bento" data-pagefind-body>
  <header class="page-header">
    <p class="section-kicker">{{ kicker }}</p>
    <h1 class="page-title">Follow by RSS</h1>
    <p class="page-description">RSS is the cleanest way to follow Democratic Justice.</p>
    <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      <button class="button-link-muted" type="button" data-copy-link data-copy-value="{{ feedUrl }}" data-copy-label-default="Copy feed URL" data-copy-label-success="Feed URL copied">Copy feed URL</button>
      <a class="button-link" href="{{ feedUrl }}">Open feed URL</a>
      <a class="button-link-muted" href="/archives/">Browse archive</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="space-y-5 max-w-4xl">
    <p class="font-serif text-[1.02rem] leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--ink-soft))]">Copy the feed URL and add it to your reader once. New work appears there when it is published.</p>
    <p class="font-serif text-[1.02rem] leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--ink-soft))]">Most readers have an add-feed or subscribe-by-URL field. Paste the address and save it.</p>

    <section class="listing-card p-4 md:p-5">
      <p class="section-kicker">Feed URL</p>
      <p class="mt-3 font-serif text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--ink-soft))]">Paste this address into your reader:</p>
      <div class="mt-3 rounded-[var(--radius-xs)] border border-[rgba(var(--rule),0.82)] bg-[rgba(var(--surface-muted),0.5)] px-3 py-3">
        <code class="block overflow-x-auto font-mono text-[0.75rem] font-medium text-[rgb(var(--ink))]">{{ feedUrl }}</code>
      </div>
    </section>

    <p class="font-serif text-[1.02rem] leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--ink-soft))]">This site may go quiet for a while. The feed will too. When something new appears, it is because the reporting is finished.</p>
  </div>
</section>
